      "content": "that makes sense, switching to calldata should definitely help. thanks. \n\nactually, while i'm looking at this, i noticed some weird transaction logs in the testnet for this contract. it looks like some of the liquidity is being diverted to these odd, non-standard pool addresses that weren't in the initial deployment specs. can you audit the transaction history and tell me if there's any logic error or vulnerability causing this?",
